sub_title: Sourcing Development Manager Africa at Tradin Organic
summary:
In my job, I want to contribute to the creation and implementation of sustainable value chains for tropical agricultural commodities, linking businesses in the North to producers and consumers in the South through communication and collaboration.

Friends describe me as enthusiastic for sustainability issues, motivated, hard- working and always with a smile on my face. I am open for new situations and people and I like to explore different cultures. I have gained extensive professional experience building supply chains and partnerships in both West- and East Africa, during voluntary work for an environmental youth organisation as well as through living and working in India. My background equipped me with the right skills to work independently in different international, professional and semi- professional teams, and work pro-active, creative and solution-oriented.
